351
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala što pratite kanal.

352
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zvali ste me Kristijan Lopec.

353
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže da, da, da.

354
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dokterica vam tijela nešto reći.

355
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čekajte.

356
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sa ona pet minuta prođuje.

357
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počnem razmišljati što je kako je.

358
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Već nekaj nervozan lupat.

359
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ona sa brat kaže.

360
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dokterica nije sad tu.

361
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zvači vas.

362
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što? Moj tata je odmah preko puta.

363
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo pogledajte kako je.

364
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ona mi je rekla.

365
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zvači vas doktrica nazad.

366
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znao da se nešto desilo.

367
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj sam se oblačio, trenio do bolice.

368
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tama parkirao auto.

369
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] I s ovaj na doktorica.

370
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže gospodin Lopec, gdje ste sad?

371
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tama parkirao. Nema slučaja.

372
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tama parkirao.

373
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže gospodin Lopec.

374
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa še opet se je nočno se previnio.

375
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tama je jako teško to mu pričati.

376
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Se bio jako vezan uz moj tata, tate.

377
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] i to ja nisam mogu svatiti to, da je to stvarno istina.

378
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se nešto baš gore je tamo.

379
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su bili tamo.

380
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja počnem plakati, vikati.

381
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije mi realno.

382
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da sam, da to nije istina, da je to sam.

383
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] A znam da je.

384
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ću manito se, kako ću s mamom se pričati, što ću moj reći.

385
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi nismo vjerovi da je to moguće.

386
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da ćemo sigurno da će vam živiti.

387
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dosta duga godina.

388
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Eto da nije bila ta jedna častna sestva koja je tamo bila, koja me je zagrljila.

389
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi je dala strašnu snagu.

390
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu ljubav koja mi je dala u tom trenutku koja je mene je bilo potrebno.

391
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Senjako zahvalim toj ženi.

392
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog hvala.

393
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ti u Berlini čekaš na nas provod.

394
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sedan ti jedna cirka.

395
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mora odtupi cvijet.

396
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] To sve.

397
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala naši glas tada, da družili smo smo mi s Hrvatima.

398
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ti organiziraš da dođi Hrvatske svečanje.

399
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato sam Hrvatsko katoličko misiju.

400
00:14:56,000 --> 00:15:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treba doći veličastni.

401
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Radoslav, a zat kako je to bilo mjesec zana, ono.

402
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Doživiš svaki dan, ne možeš se oprostiti o to.

403
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan doživiš, znaš da taj dan mora doći da moraš to sve proći.

404
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se baš on isključio od svega.

405
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, nisam mogo ni spavati.

